Install Jekyll (Standalone)

This package installs a standalone version of Jekyll, including Ruby and RubyGems.

To complete the installation, modify your PATH variable to include /opt/jekyll/bin:

    export PATH=/opt/jekyll/bin:$PATH

If you have any questions or run into trouble, check out jekyllrb.com and the Jekyll Help repository's issues (https://github.com/jekyll/jekyll-help/issues).

Happy Jekylling!
